---
// ResumeChat - AI-style conversational resume modal.
// Triggered by any element with `data-resume-chat` (or matching href="#resume-chat").
// Responses are first-person ("我") to feel like Lei is replying through an AI client.

const suggestions = [
  '你是谁？',
  '聊聊 VibeOS',
  'AI.Aspect 是什么？',
  'SkillAI Hub 是什么？',
  '工作经历',
  '怎么联系你？'
];

// Initial greeting shown when the chat opens
const greeting =
  '你好 👋 我是 Lei —— 我把自己当作一个可对话的简历放在这里。\n\n10+ 年研发经验，现在在一家跨境支付公司主导 AI 工程，同时推进个人项目 VibeOS、AI.Aspect。你可以问我任何关于我的事：经历、技术栈、在做的项目、合作方式……我会以第一人称如实回答。\n\n要不要从下面这几个问题开始？';
---

<div class="resume-chat" id="resume-chat" hidden aria-hidden="true" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="resume-chat-title">
  <div class="resume-chat-backdrop" data-resume-chat-close></div>

  <div class="resume-chat-window" role="document">
    <!-- Animated gradient border -->
    <div class="window-border" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="chat-header">
      <div class="chat-identity">
        <div class="chat-avatar">
          <span class="avatar-glyph">L</span>
          <span class="avatar-ring" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="chat-meta">
          <h2 class="chat-name" id="resume-chat-title">
            Lei <span class="chat-model">· lei-1.0</span>
          </h2>
          <div class="chat-status">
            <span class="status-led"></span>
            在线 · 以第一人称回答关于我的问题
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <button class="chat-close" type="button" data-resume-chat-close aria-label="关闭对话">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round">
          <line x1="18" y1="6" x2="6" y2="18"></line>
          <line x1="6" y1="6" x2="18" y2="18"></line>
        </svg>
      </button>
    </header>

    <!-- Messages -->
    <main class="chat-body" id="resume-chat-body" aria-live="polite" data-greeting={greeting}>
      <!-- messages get injected here -->
    </main>

    <!-- Suggestion chips -->
    <div class="chat-suggestions" id="resume-chat-suggestions">
      {suggestions.map((s) => (
        <button type="button" class="suggestion-chip" data-suggestion={s}>{s}</button>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Input -->
    <form class="chat-input" id="resume-chat-form" autocomplete="off">
      <div class="input-wrap">
        <span class="input-prefix" aria-hidden="true">›</span>
        <input
          type="text"
          id="resume-chat-input"
          name="message"
          placeholder="问点关于我的事 …"
          aria-label="输入问题"
          autocomplete="off"
        />
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="send-btn" aria-label="发送">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <line x1="22" y1="2" x2="11" y2="13"></line>
          <polygon points="22 2 15 22 11 13 2 9 22 2"></polygon>
        </svg>
      </button>
    </form>

    <div class="chat-footer">
      <span class="footer-hint">本对话由预制内容驱动 · 想真聊真人 · 直接 <button type="button" class="footer-link" data-resume-chat-action="contact">看联系方式</button></span>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  /* === Overlay === */
  .resume-chat {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 1000;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    opacity: 0;
    pointer-events: none;
    transition: opacity 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  .resume-chat[data-open='true'] {
    opacity: 1;
    pointer-events: auto;
  }

  .resume-chat[hidden] {
    display: none;
  }

  .resume-chat-backdrop {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(900px 600px at 30% 20%, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.18), transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(700px 500px at 80% 80%, rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.14), transparent 60%),
      rgba(8, 8, 14, 0.78);
    backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
  }

  /* === Window === */
  .resume-chat-window {
    position: relative;
    width: min(720px, 100%);
    height: min(720px, calc(100vh - 3rem));
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(20, 20, 30, 0.88), rgba(12, 12, 18, 0.92));
    border-radius: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.22);
    box-shadow:
      0 30px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55),
      0 0 60px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.12);
    overflow: hidden;
    transform: translateY(16px) scale(0.98);
    opacity: 0;
    transition: transform 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1), opacity 0.3s;
    isolation: isolate;
  }

  .resume-chat[data-open='true'] .resume-chat-window {
    transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
    opacity: 1;
  }

  /* Slowly flowing gradient border */
  .window-border {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    border-radius: inherit;
    padding: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,
      rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.5),
      rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.4),
      rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.4),
      rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.5));
    background-size: 300% 300%;
    -webkit-mask:
      linear-gradient(#000 0 0) content-box,
      linear-gradient(#000 0 0);
    -webkit-mask-composite: xor;
            mask-composite: exclude;
    pointer-events: none;
    animation: window-border-flow 12s linear infinite;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  @keyframes window-border-flow {
    0% { background-position: 0% 50%; }
    100% { background-position: 300% 50%; }
  }

  /* === Header === */
  .chat-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: 1.1rem 1.4rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
  }

  .chat-identity {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .chat-avatar {
    position: relative;
    width: 42px;
    height: 42px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #22d3ee);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08), 0 8px 24px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.35);
  }

  .avatar-glyph {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .avatar-ring {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -4px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1.5px dashed rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.35);
    animation: avatar-spin 14s linear infinite;
  }

  @keyframes avatar-spin {
    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
  }

  .chat-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.15rem;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .chat-name {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .chat-model {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }

  .chat-status {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }

  .status-led {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #22d3ee;
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px #22d3ee;
    animation: led-pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes led-pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.4; }
  }

  .chat-close {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 10px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .chat-close:hover {
    background: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.12);
    border-color: rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.3);
    color: #ec4899;
  }

  /* === Body / Messages === */
  .chat-body {
    flex: 1;
    overflow-y: auto;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.4rem 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    scroll-behavior: smooth;
  }

  .chat-body::-webkit-scrollbar {
    width: 6px;
  }
  .chat-body::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
    background: transparent;
  }
  .chat-body::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 3px;
  }

  .message {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    max-width: 100%;
    animation: msg-in 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1);
  }

  @keyframes msg-in {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(8px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .message.user {
    justify-content: flex-end;
  }

  .msg-avatar {
    width: 30px;
    height: 30px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  .message.ai .msg-avatar {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #22d3ee);
    color: white;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.35);
  }

  .msg-bubble {
    padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 14px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    word-break: break-word;
    max-width: 85%;
  }

  .message.ai .msg-bubble {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    border-top-left-radius: 4px;
  }

  .message.user .msg-bubble {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg,
      rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.25),
      rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.18));
    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    border-top-right-radius: 4px;
  }

  /* Inline code-ish styling within bubbles */
  .msg-bubble code {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 0.85em;
    padding: 0.05em 0.4em;
    background: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.12);
    border-radius: 4px;
    color: #22d3ee;
  }

  .msg-bubble strong {
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Blinking caret while AI is streaming */
  .msg-bubble.streaming::after {
    content: '▍';
    color: #22d3ee;
    margin-left: 2px;
    animation: caret-blink 0.9s step-end infinite;
  }

  @keyframes caret-blink {
    50% { opacity: 0; }
  }

  /* Typing indicator (three dots) */
  .typing-dots {
    display: inline-flex;
    gap: 4px;
    align-items: center;
    height: 1.2em;
  }
  .typing-dots span {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--text-tertiary);
    animation: typing-bounce 1.4s infinite ease-in-out;
  }
  .typing-dots span:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.15s; }
  .typing-dots span:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }

  @keyframes typing-bounce {
    0%, 60%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 0.4; }
    30% { transform: translateY(-4px); opacity: 1; }
  }

  /* === Suggestions === */
  .chat-suggestions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0 1.4rem 0.75rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    padding-top: 0.85rem;
  }

  .suggestion-chip {
    padding: 0.4rem 0.85rem;
    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.18);
    border-radius: 999px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    font-family: inherit;
  }

  .suggestion-chip:hover {
    background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.16);
    border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.4);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  /* === Input === */
  .chat-input {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.4rem 0.9rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
  }

  .input-wrap {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.7rem 1rem;
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border-radius: 12px;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
  }

  .input-wrap:focus-within {
    border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.5);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.12);
  }

  .input-prefix {
    color: #22d3ee;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', ui-monospace, monospace;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .input-wrap input {
    flex: 1;
    background: transparent;
    border: none;
    outline: none;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    font-family: inherit;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .input-wrap input::placeholder {
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }

  .send-btn {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #22d3ee);
    border: none;
    border-radius: 12px;
    color: white;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s, opacity 0.2s;
    box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.35);
  }

  .send-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 22px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.5);
  }

  .send-btn:disabled {
    opacity: 0.4;
    cursor: not-allowed;
    transform: none;
  }

  /* === Footer === */
  .chat-footer {
    padding: 0.6rem 1.4rem 0.9rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .footer-hint {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    text-align: center;
    display: block;
  }

  .footer-link {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: var(--accent-cyan);
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0;
    font: inherit;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-color: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.4);
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  /* === Mobile === */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .resume-chat {
      padding: 0.5rem;
    }
    .resume-chat-window {
      height: calc(100vh - 1rem);
      border-radius: 1rem;
    }
    .chat-header {
      padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
    }
    .chat-body {
      padding: 1rem 1rem 0.5rem;
    }
    .chat-suggestions,
    .chat-input,
    .chat-footer {
      padding-left: 1rem;
      padding-right: 1rem;
    }
    .msg-bubble {
      max-width: 90%;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .avatar-ring,
    .window-border,
    .status-led {
      animation: none !important;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  // === Intent matching & response bank ===
  type Intent = {
    keys: RegExp[];
    answer: string | (() => string);
    followups?: string[];
  };

  const intents: Intent[] = [
    {
      keys: [/^(你好|您好|hi|hello|hey|嗨|在吗|哈喽)/i],
      answer:
        '你好！我是 **Lei**，32 岁，10+ 年大厂研发出身，现在在一家跨境支付公司主导 AI 工程，同时在做几个个人项目。你可以问我"最近在搞什么"，或者直接挑下面的话题。',
      followups: ['你是谁？', '聊聊 VibeOS', '你的技术栈']
    },
    {
      keys: [/你是谁|介绍.*你|介绍.*自己|about you|who are you|介绍下/i],
      answer:
        '我是 **Lei**（钱磊），32 岁，上海大学本科毕业。一路在 **IBM / Ebay** 实习起步，后来在 **阿里巴巴 → 拼多多 → 美团 → 字节跳动** 做了 10 年研发，在上海、深圳、北京之间穿梭。\n\n现在我在一家**跨境支付公司**主导 AI 工程方向，同时在推进几条主线：\n\n• **VibeOS** —— AI 原生的 SDLC 操作系统\n• **AI.Aspect** —— 让 AI 工程范式像 Docker 镜像一样被分发\n• **SkillAI Hub** —— 公司内部的 MCP & AI 物料分发、托管、运营平台（已生产落地）\n\n用一句话总结自己：**一个用 10+ 年工程经验，正在把 AI 真正落到产品和组织里的人。**',
      followups: ['聊聊 VibeOS', 'AI.Aspect 是什么？', 'SkillAI Hub 是什么？']
    },
    {
      keys: [/vibeos|vibe os/i],
      answer:
        '**VibeOS** 是我现在最投入的个人项目 —— *AI-Native Operating System for the SDLC*。\n\n一句话：**用 AI 原生范式重构软件开发生命周期。**\n\n传统的 IDE / CI / 协作工具，是在工程链路上"叠加"AI；VibeOS 反过来，把 AI 当成第一公民来重新设计这条链路 —— 从产品意图、规格、编码、评审到部署，每一环都是 AI 增强的协作过程，而不是事后塞进去的功能。\n\n目标是让"想法 → 可上线产物"成为一段**连续、可观测、可回放**的对话，而不是一堆割裂的工具切换。\n\n目前研发中，欢迎一起聊想法。',
      followups: ['AI.Aspect 是什么？', 'SkillAI Hub 是什么？', '你的技术栈']
    },
    {
      keys: [/aspect|ai\.aspect|工程范式|镜像|分发ai/i],
      answer:
        '**AI.Aspect** 是我的另一个探索 —— *Distribute AI engineering paradigms like container images*。\n\n核心想法：让成熟的 AI 工程模式（提示、工具、工作流、评测、上下文规则）像 Docker 镜像一样被打包、分发、复用。\n\n任何 AI 客户端（Claude、Cursor、自研 agent…）只要 `pull` 一个 Aspect，就能即时获得一整套完整的任务能力，就像 `docker pull` 拉取一个运行时。\n\n它在解一个真问题：现在 prompt 和 agent 工作流的复用度极低，知识被锁在各自的项目里。AI.Aspect 想让这些范式像依赖一样自然流动。',
      followups: ['聊聊 VibeOS', 'SkillAI Hub 是什么？']
    },
    {
      keys: [/skillai|skill ai|skill hub|物料|公司项目|公司.*ai|跨境支付|当前公司/i],
      answer:
        '**SkillAI Hub** 是我在当前公司（一家跨境支付公司）牵头搭建的**公司级 AI 工程中枢** —— 已在生产中。\n\n要解决的痛点很现实：各团队都在做 AI，但 prompt、agent、tool、MCP server 散落在各处，知识无法沉淀、能力无法复用、上线缺少治理。\n\nSkillAI Hub 把这些"AI 物料"全部收敛到一个平台：\n\n• **分发** · 像 npm registry 一样发布 / 拉取 prompt、agent skill、MCP server\n• **托管** · 一键托管运行 MCP server，对所有 AI 客户端开放接入\n• **运营** · 版本管理、灰度发布、Eval、调用链追踪、限流、合规审计\n\n它让"某个团队踩出来的最佳实践"能被全公司复用，让 AI 在金融级合规要求下也能跑稳。\n\n你可以把它理解成：[[AI.Aspect]] 的理念在一个真实组织里的落地实例。',
      followups: ['聊聊 VibeOS', 'AI.Aspect 是什么？', '工作经历']
    },
    {
      keys: [/经历|经验|履历|工作|职业|career|experience|大厂|背景|past/i],
      answer:
